824
00:49:38,340 --> 00:49:40,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mora se biti jako oprezan

825
00:49:40,659 --> 00:49:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] u takvoj suplementaciji

826
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bi došlo do međusodnog sudaranja

827
00:49:44,599 --> 00:49:45,860
[SPEAKER_00] određenih lječanja.

828
00:49:45,860 --> 00:49:48,440
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, jeste li kad razmišljali o tome

829
00:49:48,440 --> 00:49:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] kad, znači, pred vas dođe mrtvo tijelo?

830
00:49:51,159 --> 00:49:54,900
[SPEAKER_01] Razmišljate li o tome kakav je bio život tog čovjeka

831
00:49:54,900 --> 00:49:58,079
