832
00:49:58,079 --> 00:50:00,739
[SPEAKER_01] tražite ono što treba tražiti?

833
00:50:00,739 --> 00:50:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

834
00:50:02,380 --> 00:50:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kako gledate na život, a kako na smrt?

835
00:50:05,719 --> 00:50:09,519
