917
00:54:50,219 --> 00:54:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] I to je misterija, život je misterija.

918
00:54:52,639 --> 00:54:55,280
[SPEAKER_01] Treba ga cijeniti i poštovati, je li tako?

919
00:54:55,280 --> 00:54:57,599
